### Create a New Section
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/sections/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Introduction",
  "description": "This is the introductory section."
}

### Get All Content for a Section (Section ID: 5)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/sections/5/content/

### Add Content to a Section (Section ID: 5)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/sections/5/content/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "This is a new piece of content for section 5."
}
